data.description: Do Not Let This Beautifully Updated and Spacious 4 Bed, 2 Bath, Brick Home Get Away! Hardwood Floors throughout this gorgeous Raised Ranch, Fully Renovated in 2019. Solid Built, This Home Has It All, White Custom Cabinets with Granite Countertop and Newer Stainless Steal Appliances, Lower Level Laundry with Washer and Dryer. Fully Finished Basement with Massive Family Room, 2nd Bath with Standup Shower and Massive 4th Bedroom. Separate Utility Room with Newer HVAC & Water heater. Needing just your Finishing Touches. Make this home your own stunning retreat today! Property is a "SHORT SALE" and being SOLD "AS IS"... SHORT SALE MORTGAGEE'S APPRAISAL IS IN. FINAL OFFER PRICE is subject to Bank Approval...
